Provide me with arrest records from 2010 for 'az-mcso'.
Begin!

It seems there is a misunderstanding. The task you provided involves accessing arrest records, but the tools available to me are related to the SQUAKE API, which helps businesses calculate carbon emissions and purchase climate contributions. There is no functionality to access arrest records or interact with law enforcement databases.

Since I cannot perform the task with the available tools, I will need to give up and restart.
